# TypeScript Library Conventions

- Keep public contracts strict and generic-safe; do not leak `any` through exported APIs.
- Preserve dual-package exports and declaration output when changing build or entrypoints.
- Externalize `@langchain/core`, `@langchain/langgraph`, and `zod` from the bundle.
- Prefer small deterministic helpers and explicit validation over implicit runtime behavior.
